WEBVTT

00:00.012 --> 00:01.412
Previously on The O.C...

00:01.501 --> 00:03.649
I'm doing the right thing closing down the Newport Group

00:03.727 --> 00:04.883
You're putting the past behind you.

00:04.965 --> 00:05.765
How much are we talking?

00:05.843 --> 00:07.037
You need help with the down payment.

00:07.113 --> 00:08.665
I'm not destitute, Kirsten.

00:08.746 --> 00:09.488
I'm discerning.

00:09.572 --> 00:10.576
You bought me a condo.

00:10.656 --> 00:12.168
Julie, I don't want anything from you.

00:12.262 --> 00:12.955
It's all yours.

00:13.039 --> 00:14.183
I don't have any friends.

00:14.276 --> 00:19.195
I don't trust people and so I try to control them which then drives them away.

00:19.266 --> 00:20.757
Ergo, no friends

00:20.857 --> 00:22.708
Hey, what's wrong? What did you do to her?

00:22.832 --> 00:24.345
Nothing, I'm fine

00:24.417 --> 00:26.957
Hey man, you see your girl talking to some guy you don't know..

00:27.037 --> 00:28.113
Can happen to anyone.

00:28.202 --> 00:29.986
My life just doesn't work without you.

00:30.076 --> 00:32.948
It always goes so smooth when we're together.

00:34.864 --> 00:37.196
My life just doesn't work without you.

00:44.261 --> 00:45.759
He's my brother.

00:49.374 --> 00:51.796
Please, you're killing him.

